Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Fukumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji returns to the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:20.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we give you loyal anime watchers a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:24.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There are my favorite three games from the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, in part 1, Fukumoto's Word of God echoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Number 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hell chinchiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:40.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to have it in movie 1, but shit happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time, we got it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:44.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Number 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:52.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The popular high-stakes bed makes it into Kaiji 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And number 1:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something new I cooked up for the movie called "Princess and Slave."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:00.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We've spend a lot of time going over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:06.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but I can't give you the details just yet. Check it out in the theater!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:11.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just what kinds of games will appear!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:14.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Find out in theaters this November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔性３段クルーンに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:20.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou is completely confident in the demonic third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対の自信を持つ一条\Nうわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:25.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが その自信は一転…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But that confidence is betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし上れ　上れー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:27.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:29.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:31.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:43.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジが考えた この最大難関\N難攻不落の砦 攻略法は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:45.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji has an unconventional plan to beat the impregnable third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに奇想天外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全体…\Nええっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:53.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴は傾けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:52.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He actually tilted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:58.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He tilted the whole floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フロア全体を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:59.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傾けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとビル全体を傾ける\Nくるった発想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:03.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji figured out how to tilt the entire building!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんまや　全く そのとおりや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:13.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Your crazy plan is paying off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now all you need to do is hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは当てるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当てるだけや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}Crossroads of Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！\N今日は あるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:30.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:31.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today's the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入る 入る！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:33.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can make it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長！どうです 玉の様子は？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss, how are the balls rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:51.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ分からん\Nが ともかく できることはやった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:51.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure yet. But we've done all we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,床　台　クルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:58.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The floor, the machine, the tray... They're all set to the max tilt, +10.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:03:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれを最大傾斜の\Nマックス10には…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 手前に倒すことは不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't push it any further forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが今 俺たちにできる限界だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:07.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっしゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:23.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 弱まった　いけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's slowing down... Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:27.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッソー！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッ… なんてことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:48.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れこそしたが\N今の動きは奥に流れた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:48.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It missed, but it missed to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:55.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしクルーンが手前に傾くか\N全く平らなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:57.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It could never do that if the tray was tilted forward, or even if it was level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:57.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな動きはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:04:01.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱まった玉は\Nもっと外側に沿って回転し
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:02.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A ball that's showing down should fall to the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:07.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 奥に傾いたまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So it's actually tilted back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:11.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even at max, it's not enough! I'm fucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マックスでもダメ　まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:14.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな状態で３段目にいったら\Nまたトロトロと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If he makes it back to the third tray, it'll roll right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… ダメだ　それだけは！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! That can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He may have tilted the trays toward the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:32.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵はビルを\Nクルーンの裏側に倒したが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:36.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But he has no control over it now that it's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな大技 まさか自在に\N操作できるわけじゃないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？\Nつまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:45.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So if I tilt it even further back, he won't be able to get it back how he wants it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥に倒したら 倒れっきりで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その傾斜を\N元に戻したりすることは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:45.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できないってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら かぶせてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show him how to tilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:50.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Further back! I'll push it further back too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥だ　俺も奥に… 倒す！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:52.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He pushes it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:56.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も奥に倒せば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:58.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I push it back, it combines with his tilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴が仕掛けた傾斜と重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に強力な奥傾斜になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,for a strong backward tilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:06.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば手前に当たりのある\N１段目 ２段目の通過は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:08.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That will make it even more difficult for him to make it through the first and second trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に困難になる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに それは名案です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:16.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし万が一 ３段目にいったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:16.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But what if he makes it to the third tray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:20.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It'll make it even more likely that he hits the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に大当たりの穴に入る確率が\N高くなるんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We have that one other trick, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:23.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが あったな\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:26.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２～３年前 試作した装置が\Nあったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:26.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The one we tried out a couple years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,試しに使ったら\Nその守りが あまりに露骨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:33.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The one we tried out a couple years ago? That we scrapped because it was too obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:34.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不自然なので封印した装置が…\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを使おう　あるな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:37.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ えーっと…\N多分 事務所のどこかに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's in the office, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ いや 倉庫かも…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or is it in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにしろ\Nもう使わないと思ったので…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd never use it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:51.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを探して 今すぐ持ってこい\Nはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Find it, and bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け お前らも！\Nはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You guys too! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな失敗作 使いたくなかったが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to use that failure again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けたら破滅だ\N躊躇してる場合じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I lose, I'm ruined! I can't hesitate now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できることは全てやるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:08.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to do everything I can to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして勝つ　守り切る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:12.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to protect the jackpot, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの大当たりだけは何としても…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は負けるわけにはいかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:23.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:32.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまづいて たまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't fail this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな石ころに…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not against a loser like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に２発だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got two in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッ… 冗談じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No way! I can't let this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈んで たまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな薄暗い沼\N日の当たらぬ裏カジノ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:54.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This dim Bog... This shady casino...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこの店長程度で たまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:01.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They can't be as far as I make it in life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,積み上げてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:06.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been working my way up for seven long years since I started with Teiai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:07.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛グループに入って７年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下働きからコツコツと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Working my fingers to the bone at the shittiest of shit jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:16.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kissing that creepy old bastard's ass all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:14.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの嫌なジジイにも頭を下げ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,積み上げてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリャ オリャ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか王になるために… 耐えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:27.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All for the sake of ending up on top myself someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの醜悪なジジイの気まぐれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:32.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,His nasty habits, his creepy perversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:33.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常軌を逸した いじめ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカげた余興にも\N喜々として付き合った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,his stupid games... I've played along with them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら グイグイいけ　グイッと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら 死ぬからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why? Because he's dead soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれ このジジイが死ねば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:49.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll die, and I'll get my hands on the Teiai fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの帝愛の莫大な資産
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無尽蔵の金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endless amounts of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That power will all lie in the hands of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,権力 利権を握るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒崎義裕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoshihiro Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:03.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛の次期覇王 ナンバーワン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The number one candidate to lead Teiai next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は この黒崎さんから\N特別に寵愛を受ける若きエース
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:07.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And I'm his favorite young ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:12.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll follow in his footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなった暁には\N必然的に俺も駆け上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛グループの十指に入る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll be a made man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見えているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:20.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can see that rail straight to glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その栄光へのレールは もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを消されて たまるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let him take that away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't die running this casino!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:32.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな裏カジノの店長くらいで！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわーっ！きた きた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:34.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また きたぜ ２段目！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's back in the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:39.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打てー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ　よせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:49.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入るな　入るな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入るなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわーっ！ひゃーっ！惜しい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Awwww.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:00.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわー！危ない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:59.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 あの外れ穴を\Nもしヨロヨロと抜ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:05.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If the ball had rolled around that hole, it would've made it straight into the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま 当たり穴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… 何をしている 村上は？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:12.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What the hell is Murakami doing? He's gonna be too late if he keeps wasting time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グズグズしてると 手遅れになる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早く持ってこい　早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:16.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例の装置を！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長！\Nうわっ おおっ どうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:19.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが 事務所にも店長室にも\N見当たらず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:24.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not in the main office or your office! I think it's in the safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく 倉庫ではないかと…\Nああっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 主任らが向かってます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We've sent someone to go look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々はもう一度\N事務所と店長室を…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We'll check the offices again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走れ…\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが分かってるなら 走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Run straight to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No... This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい　まずいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と奴の仕掛けで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:45.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Put together, our tilts to the back are too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥への傾斜が\Nかなりキツくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに\Nまだ２段目にくるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:51.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't I make it impossible for him to make it to the second tray?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 不可能ってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傾きだけで完全に防ぐのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't I make the tilt a perfect defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに奥への傾斜で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:59.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can make it a lot harder to make it in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:00.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手前側の当たり穴に\Nいきにくくはできるが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来てしまった玉はダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but I can't do anything about balls coming at the right angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外側から\N流れ込むようにして入るのを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:07.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't keep them from coming up the outside and then rolling in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,防ぐことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:09.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:19.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ　やめろ　やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This can't be the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は終われない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　お前だ\Nお前なら いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:27.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Why can't it just happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は単なるギャンブル中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:33.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You'd just a worthless gambling addict with no future!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もない　お前の未来には何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えろ　消えろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Disappear! Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Disappear! Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You should just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら お前が消えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は… 俺は\N見返さなきゃならないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:51.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's people I need to get back at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:55.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて俺を見下したバカどもを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The idiots who looked down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:11:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その思い上がった勘違い\N傲慢を正さなきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:11:00.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to throw their misunderstandings and their hubris back in their face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:05.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their mocking, their prejudice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:05.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らの俺に対するバカげた誤解\N思い込みを！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らしめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:13.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show them who the stupid, shallow ones are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:13.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちが愚かか\Nどっちが浅はかで程度が低いか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:16.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}I need to prove it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,証明しなければならないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやあ もう…\Nあれ 一条じゃねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}Oh, hey, isn't that Ichijou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:20.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:19.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}Yeah, it is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ やっぱり一条だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関谷だよ 高校の時 一緒だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}I'm Sekiya! Remember me from high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カジノ？\N一条 カジノに勤めてんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You run a casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ\Nなに？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:35.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What, couldn't you find anything better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなとこにしか いけなかったの\Nあっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought you studied harder than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勉強できたのにな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり厳しいか 大学行かないと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess you really get screwed if you don't go to college, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと トイレ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった やった　ざまあみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look at that loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やな奴だったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's because he's such a creeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:07.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったよ 落ちぶれて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虚業じゃん カジノなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A casino? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実態ないもんな\Nそうそう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he really needs to find himself a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと しっかりしたとこ\N入んなきゃ 就職は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その点 俺たちは安心だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At least we've got ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一部上場の銀行と証券会社に\N内定だもんな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:21.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got this internship lined up at an investment bank—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った 勝った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち組だよ 勝ち組！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:30.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ バカが！\N見えてねえな クズども
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those fools don't even realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実態が見えてねえのは\Nそっちなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:34.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They don't see what's really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのジジイは大嫌いだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:39.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't like the old man, but he's dead-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:39.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴の言うことは的確 的を射ている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たち 金持ちとは何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you call "rich"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:53.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金持ちとしての最低条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:55.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you think is necessary to be "rich"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:56.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必須条件を聞いておる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 何だ それは？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億円… くらいですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Around a hundred million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？\N預金が… １億円くらい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Around a hundred million in the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う 違う\Nそういう話ではないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:14.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億円が10億円でも\N時には空しいものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hundred million, a billion, that'll run out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなものでは守れん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That much isn't enough to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムニャ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が命よ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:34.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now the politicians have my life in their hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の状況は 上の政治家どもに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生殺与奪を握られている状態だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らが交渉を誤れば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:39.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All they need to do is sign off on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさり我が頭上で\N核が さく裂するだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:42.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and a nuke could go off right over my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:47.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What good is money with that hanging over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その事態に対応できずして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何が金持ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守らにゃならん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:56.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I must be protected! I must be able to live a life of privileged luxury even if that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ら特権者は\Nそういう事態になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,快適にリッチに\N暮らしていかねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを成し遂げてこそ 富豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:02.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金持ちというものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうは思わんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You mean a shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:08.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シェルターですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:13.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of thing the government should provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　まあ本来なら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国が配備すべきものだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらが望むのは\N普通のシェルターじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I want something better than a normal shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:20.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What I'm building now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが今 建設しておるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:25.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨大シェルター都市 地下帝国\Nうおっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is a massive vault. An underground empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこには スーパー 病院\Nゴルフ場 カジノ 何でもある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Inside it, stores, hospitals, golf courses, casinos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:34.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those loyal to Teiai will have everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:34.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が帝愛グループに\N忠誠を尽くす者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが特別に認めた者のみが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:41.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My handpicked followers will be able to survive there in comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこで安心して暮らし\N生き延びることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:47.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ そのうち\Nみんなも気づくじゃろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:46.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, they'll all realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:51.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが言ったことが\Nまさに まことだったとな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Realize that I speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:56.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時を境に\N預金も国債もゴミクズ同然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:56.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Realize that society's savings accounts and bonds are worth less than dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:15:01.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巨大シェルター都市 及び\N強大な力を持つ者こそが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:15:03.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He with a shelter and power at his fingertips will be the strongest of the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最高の強者となる\Nあっ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これもまた 至極当然な話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:08.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It'll be clear as day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll show you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:16.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えておけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざとなった時\Nお前らや お前らの家族は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:24.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When it happens, I'm not letting you or yours in, no matter how much you bow and scrape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:24.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に入れない\Nどんなに頭を下げてもな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:38.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't let that fade away! Not here, not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:35.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えるわけにはいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところで消えるわけには…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:41.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には あるんだ 未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輝かしい未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A glittering future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えろ　耐えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold out! Just hold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:55.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My final weapon... My last ray of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終兵器 俺の最後の頼みの綱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの防御を作動させる\Nリモコンが来るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hold out until I can activate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えるんだ　俺と奴の仕掛け
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:05.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This double tilt must work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この二重の奥への傾斜で…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた きたー！\Nまた きたぜ ２段目に！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the second tray again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:15.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't make it to the third tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくな\N３段目に いかせたらダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:21.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The backward tilt makes the third tray more likely to roll a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目は傾斜で玉が奥に流れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:23.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ入りやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:25.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５分の１ってことは あり得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:27.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not even one in five anymore! It's one in two or three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:29.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３分の１か ２分の１\N突確頼みしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:33.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have to stop him in the first or second tray, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:35.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとしても\N１段目か この２段目で！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ 惜しい 惜しい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aww, that sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:43.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけいけ！へこたれるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:45.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're still fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しだ　もう少し
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…\N終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That ten million is finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万が…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:23.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てことは あと1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So he's only get ten million left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:27.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it. His last Paqy card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラスト… あれがラストパッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耐えた… ここまでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I made it... I'm still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 俺が奴の奥の傾斜にかぶせて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I think that double tilt did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に奥の傾斜を きつくしたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:41.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I started it just as he was getting into the second half of that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:41.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残金500万と表示された直後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That means that he didn't make the third tray once in five million!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり500万は一度も\N３段目に いかせなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The double tilt is doing the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守り切った\N二重の奥への傾斜で何とか…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't rely on that other remote showing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう いつ来るか分からない\N例の最終リモコンは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あてにできない　こうなりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:59.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I may have to hold out with just this double tilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:18:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この二重の奥への傾斜で\N耐えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:04.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:09.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるな\Nもう くる頃だ　もう！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:05.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:07.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can feel it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り 1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's got ten million left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million! 2,500 more shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと1000万 2500発
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:26.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと2500発
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only 2,500 more shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:30.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この2500発を耐えれば 勝ち！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:31.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I survive those 2,500, I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くるな くるな…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:31.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:34.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay out! Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時 カイジと一条\Nこの２人のどちらにも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:46.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right now, both Kaiji and Ichijou can rise to heaven or fall to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け 破滅があり 勝利もあった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが２人とも\N持っていなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:52.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Neither of them have a decisive advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その決定的な何かを…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆえに はね転がる\N銀玉の気まぐれで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:59.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Both their fates rest on nothing more but the arc of the balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすく どちらにも転んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:06.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 その勝利の行方を\N決める何かは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:10.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Neither can rely on anything more than their natural luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人が生まれながらに\N持っている運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This may be destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宿運の差かもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして それは生まれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:18.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their lives come down to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,努力など関係なく\Nただ生まれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:22.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And Ichijou's luck takes the upper hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条が上回った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They disappear in waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:42.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消える　消える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's balls fall into the void fruitlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ無為に消えていく玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ　何だよ これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得るのか こんなこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:54.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This should be impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と奴との\N奥への傾斜がかぶさって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:20:01.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know it should be hard to make it to the third tray with both of us tilting in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:01.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目に いきにくいのは\N分かるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 500万
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:06.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But at least one in five million's worth should make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:08.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,500万に１発ぐらい\Nいってもいいはずだ ３段目に！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:11.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There should be enough of a chance for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるはずだ それぐらいの確率は！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:20.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yet I've shot over ten million in, and they've all been sucked into the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに もう1000万以上\N打ち込んでるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吸い込まれちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ことごとく手前で…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:25.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're all rolling in front! Dammit! Has it abandoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ 見放されたか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:30.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's do-or-die, I'm on the edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この正念場\N崖っぷちの勝負どころで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運 ツキに…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Has my luck finally run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい なんか怪しいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:41.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメじゃん まるで…\Nいかねえよ ３段目に…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This shouldn't be happening like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not making it to the third tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:45.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji now has only two million left! Only 500 shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:46.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてカイジ 残金200万\N500発を切る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 終わっちまうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:54.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please... I don't need a lot of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むよ\N強運なんかじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking for a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:00.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇跡も要らない\N平運 ほんのちょっとした運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit... I just need one thing to go my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけでいい　起こってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all I need! Please, make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:07.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just make things happen how they normally should!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:07.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごく普通の現象 確率！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's doom closes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迫る！壊滅 決着の時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが勝負はまだ…\Nまだ ついていない！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:21.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But it isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけることができるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:26.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can Kaiji find a way to survive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生還への突破口を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:28.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突破口！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A survival strategy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:35.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please... I don't need a lot of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking for a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:56.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit... I just need one thing to go my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:58.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:00.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please, make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:05.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just make things happen how they normally should!
